Why I teamed up with @Sweat to bring you Reboot üëá 

Over the years I've had SO many friends, clients and community members talk to me about their setbacks and all the times they had to start over but didn't know where to begin...

After giving birth to Arna I finally understood what they were experiencing. What I wanted to be able to do vs what my body was capable of couldn't have been further apart... it was a mental and emotional battle as much as it was a physical one and I honestly felt so lost during this time! 

I wanted to create something for every person who has ever felt this way, so no one had to feel alone in their journey again. Think of Reboot as your four-week toolkit designed to set you up for long-term success. All the thinking has been done for you, so all you need to do is show up!!

The book has a movement plan, recipes, journal pages and pep talks from me with different focuses each week. I speak about mindset, motivation, fitness, momentum and SOO much more to help you develop a powerful and positive relationship with fitness to achieve YOUR goals üí™ 

If you're ready for a change, go check out Reboot via the link in my bio. ‚ù§Ô∏è
